PURPOSE:-
--------
To test that proper hello message generation and processing in an
IPv4 scenario.



SCENARIO:-
---------

       
             [1]           [2]
                                       
  
  
                             
Nodes 1 and 2 are placed in ad-hoc manner. 
Network is  are running OLSRv2-NIIGATA as routing protocol.

Application:
------------
One CBR application is configured between Node 1 and Node 2



RUN:-
----
Run '<QUALNET_HOME>/bin/qualnet hello-test.config'.


DESCRIPTION OF THE FILES:-
-------------------------
1. hello-test.app           - QualNet configuration file for application input.
2. hello-test.config        - QualNet configuration input file.
3. hello-test.expected.stat - QualNet statistics collection.
4. hello-test.nodes         - QualNet Configuration file for node position input.
5. README                   - This file.

